comments:
Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Bilton with 
    Harrogate. Abolished 1.4.1938 and divided between the parishes of Harrogate and 
    Knaresborough.

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Harrogate and 
    Bilton.

Created 1894 from the parts of the parishes of Bilton with Harrogate 
    and Pannal in Harrogate Municipal Borough. See also Table 2, note (g).

That part which until 1.4.1938 formed part of the parish of Follifoot. See 
    also Table 2, note (f).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Knaresborough. 
    See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Scriven with 
    Tentergate. See also Table 2, note (g).

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Tentergate and 
    Scriven.

Created 15.4.1896 out of the parish of Bilton. Abolished 1.4.1938 
    and added to the parish of Harrogate.

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Scriven with 
    Tentergate. Abolished 30.9.1895 and added to the parish of Knaresborough.
